### Energy Analysis
### Returns energy statistics for a date range.
POST {{base_url}}/power_service/v1/site/energy_analysis
Content-Type: application/json
Model-Type: DESKTOP
App-Name: anker_power
Os-Type: android
Country: {{country}}
Timezone: {{timezone}}
x-auth-token: {{auth_token}}
gtoken: {{gtoken}}

{
  "site_id": "{{site_id}}",
  "device_sn": "{{device_sn}}",
  "type": "week",
  "start_time": "2025-01-01",
  "end_time": "",
  "device_type": "solar_production"
}

> {%
    client.test("Energy analysis successful", function () {
        client.assert(response.status === 200, "Expected 200 OK");
    });
%}

###
